残りわずかだった。","ep":4,"sort":4,"id":1663150,"subject_id":565304,"comment":11,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-04-29","name":"王様、奮闘する。","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"ブラルドが集めたメンバーにはイライジャやルーカスの姿もあった。アーサーとジャスミンは即席のパーティーで『恐怖の墓地』の奥底へと潜っていく。その最下層には巨大な魔石があるという……だが、ダンジョン内のトラップやビーストの襲撃で犠牲者が出てしまう。事前に下調べをしたと語っていたブラルドだが、その様子はどこかおかしくて……。","ep":5,"sort":5,"id":1663151,"subject_id":565304,"comment":11,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-05-06","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":6,"sort":6,"id":1663152,"subject_id":565304,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-05-13","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":7,"sort":7,"id":1663153,"subject_id":565304,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-05-20","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":8,"sort":8,"id":1663154,"subject_id":565304,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-05-27","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":9,"sort":9,"id":1663155,"subject_id":565304,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-06-03","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":10,"sort":10,"id":1663156,"subject_id":565304,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-06-10","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":11,"sort":11,"id":1663157,"subject_id":565304,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0},{"airdate":"2026-06-17","name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","desc":"","ep":12,"sort":12,"id":1663158,"subject_id":565304,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":0}],"updatedAt":"2026-05-01T14:36:50.007Z"},"565701":{"detail":{"date":"2026-07-08","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/85/7f/565701_JKCaL.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/85/7f/565701_JKCaL.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/85/7f/565701_JKCaL.jpg","medium":"https://lain.